code: public static DataFrameTransformState randomDataFrameTransformState() {     return new DataFrameTransformState(randomFrom(IndexerState.values()), randomPosition(), randomLongBetween(0, 10)). }

private static Map<String, Object> randomPosition() {     if (randomBoolean()) {         return null.     }     int numFields = randomIntBetween(1, 5).     Map<String, Object> position = new HashMap<>().     for (int i = 0. i < numFields. i++) {         Object value.         if (randomBoolean()) {             value = randomLong().         } else {             value = randomAlphaOfLengthBetween(1, 10).         }         position.put(randomAlphaOfLengthBetween(3, 10), value).     }     return position. }
